{"tid":753804,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳凱琳父母聞抱孫笑咪咪","createTime":"2018-07-24T02:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T15:07:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d23bd25be97355b398ae31feb0da9d87f148545e","tid":753804,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"現年27歲的陳凱琳（Grace）有傳下月將會與今年48歲的鄭嘉穎結婚，最開心的當然是即將嫁女的陳爸爸，昨日下午2時許，Grace的父母及姊姊剛嘆完茶，返回九龍塘獨立屋寓所。<br />\n陳爸爸一馬當先，行在最前，當聽見記者講「恭喜！恭喜！」時，即刻笑容滿面。被問到囡囡Grace何時註冊結婚時，陳爸爸保持口密說：「我都唔知，未同我哋講呀！呢排少見（嘉穎）啲。」提到有傳陳爸爸好快抱孫時，陳爸爸最初扮聽不到，再三追問下，陳爸爸才笑說：「抱孫？我個女都未結婚。」而一直在旁的太太全程笑得合不攏嘴。問到禮金一事，陳爸爸即擰頭說：「我老婆開唔到聲，把聲沙咗。」另外，有傳Grace已經跟嘉穎同居，所以很少返屋企住，陳爸爸即代女兒澄清絕無其事，入屋前一家人亦很有禮貌地跟在場傳媒說再見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/101246_4ed3ded406ae317cf2c35b94748e2098.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F101246_4ed3ded406ae317cf2c35b94748e2098.png&h=7e5edd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGrace的父母與姊姊昨日一同回家，講到抱孫，陳父即笑笑口說個女未嫁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180724/20458133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458133&d=yNkmeMlVCs07GOpqs1huS10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=060c9e57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458133&h=854009e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180724/20458133</a>"},{"pid":"30bd47d9085ff2c9b0c05913acb9a106a654601a","tid":753804,"uid":31841,"like":40,"dislike":5,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"有孫又點<br />\n同佢都冇血緣關係"},{"pid":"cd4494f49e4885d3cb43bdf29b45db3f589e966a","tid":753804,"uid":99700,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"30bd47d9085ff2c9b0c05913acb9a106a654601a","tid":753804,"uid":3